You get the same immersive
Hangouts.

01:17:12.060 --> 01:17:14.940
You get all the new navigation,
the new profiles.

01:17:14.940 --> 01:17:20.110
And it looks just gorgeous
on that retina display.

01:17:20.110 --> 01:17:25.160
So that's the Google+ tablet
app rolling out for Android

01:17:25.160 --> 01:17:28.400
today, available for
the iPad very soon.

01:17:28.400 --> 01:17:29.380
What do you think?

