01:24:42.200 --> 01:24:44.730
I guess you can see the brunch
is going on over there.

01:24:44.730 --> 01:24:46.570
And they just stream
in real time.

01:24:46.570 --> 01:24:51.440
That's a lot of fun to just
watch as it happens.

01:24:51.440 --> 01:24:55.070
Now, in addition to having
this view, we built in

01:24:55.070 --> 01:24:56.120
a slide show view.

01:24:56.120 --> 01:24:59.100
So, Matt, if you go to the top
there, it says, play the live

01:24:59.100 --> 01:25:00.150
slide show.

01:25:00.150 --> 01:25:04.160
And if you click during the
event, we'll go to an

01:25:04.160 --> 01:25:07.060
absolutely gorgeous full-screen
light box.

01:25:07.060 --> 01:25:10.720
And your guests' photos will
appear instantly after they've

01:25:10.720 --> 01:25:11.590
taken those pictures.

01:25:11.590 --> 01:25:12.510
Isn't that just great?

