about after the event.

01:25:30.420 --> 01:25:33.600
After the event, what happens
when the guests go home?

01:25:33.600 --> 01:25:35.830
Well, we reminisce about the
event, we might think of

01:25:35.830 --> 01:25:37.990
something that was very special,
and we try to hold on

01:25:37.990 --> 01:25:39.160
to those memories.

01:25:39.160 --> 01:25:42.320
Because getting everyone's
photos and videos, we've given

01:25:42.320 --> 01:25:43.280
up on that.

01:25:43.280 --> 01:25:44.560
Well, not anymore.

01:25:44.560 --> 01:25:48.360
As you saw with Party Mode,
Google+ will send emails to

01:25:48.360 --> 01:25:51.140
