01:27:09.880 --> 01:27:12.380
the photo that got the most
engagement from his wedding,

01:27:12.380 --> 01:27:14.600
the most engagement
from his guests.

01:27:14.600 --> 01:27:16.360
Absolutely gorgeous.

01:27:16.360 --> 01:27:20.160
Now in addition, if there was
a photo of you and you are

01:27:20.160 --> 01:27:22.700
tagged in a photo, your
photos would be there

01:27:22.700 --> 01:27:24.030
