01:27:24.030 --> 01:27:26.250
Now, what if you have a friend
and you just want to see

01:27:26.250 --> 01:27:27.660
photos that they took?

01:27:27.660 --> 01:27:30.280
Well, you can see the different
photographers who

01:27:30.280 --> 01:27:32.890
had Party Mode turned on
and who contributed.

