01:27:40.790 --> 01:27:45.200
When you consider what Google+
Events does for before,

01:27:45.200 --> 01:27:49.110
during, and after an event, it
really speaks to what we're

01:27:49.110 --> 01:27:50.870
trying to do with
Google overall.

