accelerometers, and a compass.

01:40:31.170 --> 01:40:34.880
So it's aware of its location
with respect to my body and is

01:40:34.880 --> 01:40:41.740
also aware of its location in
the broader physical world.

01:40:41.740 --> 01:40:44.450
And lastly and very importantly,
it has multiple

01:40:44.450 --> 01:40:46.750
radios for data communication.

01:40:46.750 --> 01:40:49.200
To give you a bit about the
history of our group, we

01:40:49.200 --> 01:40:52.560
started about two, two and a
half years ago to incorporate

01:40:52.560 --> 01:40:55.810
