together--

01:41:05.065 --> 01:41:08.010
we're sort of a hacky,
informal group--

01:41:08.010 --> 01:41:10.690
to get the technology on
people's bodies to make it

01:41:10.690 --> 01:41:13.410
wearable and test
out the ideas.

01:41:13.410 --> 01:41:16.130
So we started from this point
two, two and a half years ago.

01:41:16.130 --> 01:41:19.040
And through a lot of hard
work by our team, and

01:41:19.040 --> 01:41:23.460
experimentation, we made
progress and reduced the form

01:41:23.460 --> 01:41:26.170
factor to what you see here.

01:41:26.170 --> 01:41:29.670
