01:53:11.340 --> 01:53:14.690
she's growing, how
she's changing.

01:53:14.690 --> 01:53:18.190
With babies, it's really hard
to grab the right moments.

01:53:18.190 --> 01:53:21.500
A smile just lasts for a few
