01:55:04.380 --> 01:55:06.940
compelling since we made
these and started using

01:55:06.940 --> 01:55:08.770
them out and about.

01:55:08.770 --> 01:55:11.030
We've just found that
to be amazing.

01:55:11.030 --> 01:55:15.490
The second is it's actually one
of the things we can show

01:55:15.490 --> 01:55:22.342
you, because you all can't
experience what it's like to

01:55:22.342 --> 01:55:23.990
have all this information
available right

01:55:23.990 --> 01:55:25.670
here just like that.

01:55:25.670 --> 01:55:28.300
And so there are other kinds of
things that we use it for.

01:55:28.300 --> 01:55:32.440
But it's hard to demonstrate.

01:55:32.440 --> 01:55:34.890
I guess you could put one glass
on top of another glass,

01:55:34.890 --> 01:55:37.620
and then you'd see what
we experience.

01:55:37.620 --> 01:55:40.640
But that might be awkward.

01:55:40.640 --> 01:55:43.580
So you haven't had a chance
to experience it.

01:55:43.580 --> 01:55:46.620
And third, we're a pretty
small team.

01:55:46.620 --> 01:55:51.360
And we've only had so much time
to try various kinds of

01:55:51.360 --> 01:55:52.240
functionality.

01:55:52.240 --> 01:55:55.540
And in fact, every day, we've
been getting great ideas from

01:55:55.540 --> 01:55:58.260
inside, from outside, from
all around the world.

01:55:58.260 --> 01:56:02.250
And that's why we really want
to involve all of you.

01:56:02.250 --> 01:56:05.690
This developer community is
going to be key to us.

01:56:05.690 --> 01:56:10.800
And that's why today, I'd like
to announce the Google Glass

01:56:10.800 --> 01:56:12.050
Explorer Edition.

01:56:16.030 --> 01:56:18.050
It's going to be something that
we'd like to get in the

01:56:18.050 --> 01:56:21.350
hands of people who are really
passionate about it, who want

01:56:21.350 --> 01:56:24.290
to be among the earliest
to get this device.

01:56:24.290 --> 01:56:27.320
This is not going to be a
consumer device in a sense.

01:56:27.320 --> 01:56:29.045
It's going to be rough
around the edges.

01:56:32.220 --> 01:56:34.380
You have to want to be
on the bleeding edge.

01:56:34.380 --> 01:56:36.080
And that's what this is
really designed for.

